                    Organize your fictional worlds and manage privacy settings
                  <% when 'Character' %>
                    Develop protagonists, antagonists, and supporting cast
                  <% when 'Location' %>
                    Build cities, regions, buildings, and important places
                  <% when 'Item' %>
                    Create weapons, artifacts, tools, and magical objects
                  <% end %>
